collectionMetadata.name: Number of Overseas Dental and Pharmacy Schools in the Schedule
collectionMetadata.description:
Overseas Dental and Pharmacy schools recognised by Singapore Dental Council and Singapore Pharmacy Council respectively.

The list of recognised overseas pharmacy schools can be found at the Singapore Dental Council website:
http://www.healthprofessionals.gov.sg/content/dam/hprof/sdc/docs/publication/THE%20SCHEDULE%20%28020108%29.pdf 

The list of recognised overseas pharmacy schools can be found at the Singapore Pharmacy Council website: http://www.healthprofessionals.gov.sg/content/dam/hprof/spc/docs/Others/SPC_Recognised_Qualifications.pdf
